On our first day in Barcelona, we crashed in our place in Poblenou and hit the Rambla de Poblenou for some grub.  We found this place on Yelp and it did not disappoint.  We had the fried fish, mussels, grilled prawns, chorizo and spicy potatoes w/mayo (yum!).  It was all definitely worth it...and the price was great as well!
